videos.description: Indiana's Troy Williams gets loose on the baseline and throws down a vicious one-handed dunk in the Hoosiers' rivalry game.
videos.headline: Williams baseline dunk gets Assembly Hall rocking

videos.description: 1H (9:56) IND Yogi Ferrell made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Y. Ferrell made Three Point Jumper.

videos.description: Indiana's Troy Williams makes the steal and throws down another vicious dunk that has the crowd in Bloomington going wild.
videos.headline: Williams keeps dunking, Hoosiers keep going crazy
